                <div class="project__about">
                    <p>The main theme of this project revolves around <strong>false memories</strong>, coupled with the <strong>creation of fiction that could critically</strong> reconsider our position as students at the Faculty of Fine Arts, University of Lisbon. This reflection is made possible through the crafting of a fictional narrative, materialized in the creation of a persona (Camila) in three stages of her life. The speculative scenario is transposed into our reality through <strong>audio elements</strong>, <strong>visual components (videos and physical objects)</strong>, and digital aspects (Camilaâ€™s computer files). All elements complement each other to function in synchrony within a carefully designed <strong>Project Room</strong> experience, <strong>lasting for 15 minutes.</strong></p>

