                            <img class="project__carousel-item" src="assets/img/portfolio/rather-project/rather_landing-page.jpg" alt="an image of rathe's website landing page. rather is written in the middle with a black whole circle behind it.">
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <h3>Why are we proud of it?</h3>
                    <p>H.C.A.T.M.W.A.T.F was a very complete and multifaceted project. Besides thorough research on a very complex topic, we had to create an immersive experience. This demanded the creation of a detailed narrative that revolved around the future of student designers through 3 different timelines. To bring this story and persona to life, we developed an experience in a physical space with physical objects synced with 3 videos and 3 different audios that had a written script read by 3 different AI voices.<br><br> Overall, this project had a lot of devices, objects, and nuances that really came to life when put together. You can see all about it on the project website.</p>

